headline: ABNB Q4 Deep Dive: Product Innovation and Global Expansion Drive Momentum
summary: Online accommodations platform Airbnb (NASDAQ:ABNB) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 12% year on year to $2.78 billion. Guidance for next quarter’s revenue was optimistic at $2.61 billion at the midpoint, 3% above analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.56 per share was 14.3% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
